<tr>
<td>平移（筛选，取样）</td>
<td>$\int_{-\infty }^{+\infty }{\text{f}\left( t \right)\text{ }\!\!\delta\!\!\text{ }\left( t-T \right)\text{d}t}=\text{f}\left( T \right)$</td>
</tr>
